name: Light Machinery
desc: Precision-engineered machines and tools used in light manufacturing and assembly. Essential for producing consumer goods and smaller-scale industrial components.

name: Structural Components
desc: Bulk structural parts and frames used in heavy assemblies and substructures.

name: Precision Components
desc: High-precision machined parts made from rare metals, essential for advanced systems and precision-heavy assemblies. Used in the manufacture of components for machinery, electronics, and specialized equipment requiring exact tolerances and durability.

name: Subassembly Parts
desc: Pre-assembled modules combining light and precision components. Ready for final assembly.

name: Light Components
desc: Light, labor-intensive components used in consumer goods and light industrial products. Forms the backbone of everyday manufacturing and assembly.
